    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/364bcb717d2c2f6f228fe45401768975.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/364bcb717d2c2f6f228fe45401768975.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/364bcb717d2c2f6f228fe45401768975.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/29ee248bb289056f496dc8c77768d605.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=127 /></span><br>嘿，人类，是我，卡尔顿！我是菲比最信任的伙伴……要我说的话，我也是最酷的机械臂。下面，我想为你介绍一下菲比和她的最新发明：软盘骑士！ <br><br>现在你要问了，那谁是菲比呀？她是位很有天赋的发明家。她的任务是：存足够多的钱，好搬出父母的房子。小镇里奇奇怪怪的工作啊，简直太多了，菲比实在分身乏术，所以，软盘骑士就派上用场了！ <br><br>你的麾下将聚集种类繁多的软盘骑士，你可以从中挑选，打造自己的独特风格。你还可以随心混合和搭配各种新潮的卡牌组合，来制定获胜策略。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/4665e89a136f6346d70d5e53f2d59050.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=138 /></span><br><strong>回合策略玩法与卡牌构建的巧妙融合。</strong><br>将两种大家耳熟能详的游戏类型融合成全新的风格！利用精心挑选的卡组，带领你的骑士们横扫战场，赢得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/0ad23c90a8f74bcd913b5e157fb45999.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=586 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/0ad23c90a8f74bcd913b5e157fb45999.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/0ad23c90a8f74bcd913b5e157fb45999.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>生气勃勃的幻想世界，复古科技与魔法并存。</strong><br>踏入插画师Marlowe Dobbe（曾经担纲《骰子地下城》美术）精心刻画的幻想大陆，在郁郁葱葱的沃土密林、危机四伏的火山重峦、寒冷彻骨的冰洞及神秘莫测的迷雾森林尽情探索。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/b9763b5e513bd93cbe7cac6b82fcc2ad.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/b9763b5e513bd93cbe7cac6b82fcc2ad.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/b9763b5e513bd93cbe7cac6b82fcc2ad.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>找到属于你的软盘骑士作战风格！</strong><br>每个单位都拥有独一无二的玩法和技能，能够在战斗中生成特殊的卡牌，为你创造无限可能。<br><br>每个软盘骑士卡组都代表着不同的阵营和策略：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>植物卡组</strong> - 升级你的技能、治疗队友，并获取地形优势。<br></li><li><strong>怪兽卡组</strong> - 增加护甲，用生命值换取各种增益效果。<br></li><li><strong>坏蛋卡组</strong> - 三个词语：卑鄙、恶毒、迅捷。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/05f0c38380532aaf6f5369d6dc40f945.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/05f0c38380532aaf6f5369d6dc40f945.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/05f0c38380532aaf6f5369d6dc40f945.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>制定完美抽卡策略。</strong><br>无论是经验丰富的策略专家还是初出茅庐的新手，都可以通过酣畅淋漓的战斗和数不胜数的卡牌组合保持敏锐的洞见，从而找到绝佳的策略。充分利用那些可以增加和翻出辅助性牌的卡牌，打出天衣无缝的连击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/fe40db6a439a5909f623ee27a13aad98.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/fe40db6a439a5909f623ee27a13aad98.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/fe40db6a439a5909f623ee27a13aad98.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>跟随音乐节奏欢快律动。</strong><br>伴着Grahm Nesbitt（《花园故事》音乐制作人）令人耳目一新的复古匠心乐曲，在战场中翩翩起舞吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/21ac930dd5d4499597889db140f98571.poster.avif?t=1746806768\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/21ac930dd5d4499597889db140f98571.webm?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1057800/extras/21ac930dd5d4499597889db140f98571.mp4?t=1746806768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
